<div class="status-header">
    <div class="tag" style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #166534;">COMPLETED</div>
    <h1>Deal Settled Successfully</h1>
    <p>Order #{{orderId}} has been marked as COMPLETED.</p>
</div>

<div class="highlight-box">
    <p style="color: #475569; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        All lifecycle milestones for this trade are finished. The final payout has been released, and the transaction is now closed.
    </p>
    <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Order Number</div>
        <div class="info-value">#{{orderId}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Total Trade Value</div>
        <div class="info-value">₹{{grandTotal}}</div>
    </div>
</div>

<p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 11px; text-align: center;">
    Thank you for trading through BulkMandi. We hope to serve you again soon!
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
    <a href="{{ctaUrl}}" class="btn">View Order History</a>
</div>
